          <a href="/book/show/11588.The_Shining"><img id="more_book_11588" alt="The Shining" title="The Shining" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1353277730l/11588._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
